My brother and I die when that
commercial comes on.

189
00:12:37,632 --> 00:12:38,581
So brilliant!

190
00:12:39,092 --> 00:12:40,088
You think so?

191
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:41,838
Yeah, don't you?

192
00:12:42,846 --> 00:12:43,925
Well I...

193
00:12:44,056 --> 00:12:44,802
What?

194
00:12:44,973 --> 00:12:48,556
- That's actually my commercial.
- Your commercial?

195
00:12:48,727 --> 00:12:51,479
Well, That's what I do.
I make television commercials.

196
00:12:52,773 --> 00:12:55,644
I don't even know you and
I've already called you brilliant.

197
00:12:56,151 --> 00:12:58,440
Makes me feel slightly better
about being a sell-out...

198
