less sure of that...

945
00:59:24,895 --> 00:59:28,430
But... then I ran into
this girl at the cafe.

946
00:59:29,108 --> 00:59:30,103
Gorgeous...

947
00:59:30,234 --> 00:59:31,099
Funny...

948
00:59:31,235 --> 00:59:32,563
Blonde...
- Hey!

949
00:59:32,695 --> 00:59:35,067
I'm kidding... I'm kidding!
- That's not nice.

950
00:59:35,531 --> 00:59:40,110
And... I was 'sure' that I wanted
to talk to her.

951
00:59:41,078 --> 00:59:42,738
I wanted to get to
know her.

952
00:59:43,497 --> 00:59:45,823
And the more I got to know her,
the more I became sure...

953
00:59:46,000 --> 00:59:48,538
...that I've never met anyone
like her.

954
00:59:49,754 --> 00:59:52,957
And that everything with her is
better that anything without her.

955
00:59:54,634 --> 00:59:56,212
I'm better with her.

956
00:59:57,887 --> 00:59:59,002
So...

957
00:59:59,889 --> 01:00:02,677
I guess I've never really been sure
about anything except you.

958
01:00:04,311 --> 01:00:05,935
I'm 'sure' about you.

959
01:00:08,023 --> 01:00:10,478
